
GBInfo Project
--------------

Get book info details from isbndb.com

Author: Rosa Durante <rosunix@gmail.com>

Installation:
------------

. Install setuptools and virtualenv:

sudo apt-get install virtualenv setuptools

. Create a virtualenv for this project:

virtualenv venv-gbinfo --no-site-packages

. Activate virtualenv:

source venv-gbinfo/bin/activate

. Get source code from github (read-only):

git clone git://github.com/rosUnix/GBInfo.git

. Install django:

easy_install django

. Install httplib2

easy_install httplib2

. Run project:

cd GBInfo
python manage.py runserver

. Open http://localhost:8000 and enjoy!